             was indicted for <rs id="t17831210-3-off17" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17831210-3-off17" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17831210-3-off17" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17831210-3-cd18" type="crimeDate">29th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-3-off17 t17831210-3-cd18"></join> last, two black geldings, price 40 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-3-victim94" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
